@startuml Cpanchal1_Chatbot101-with-AWS-Lambda
left to right direction
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}

actor "User" as User
rectangle "Webex Teams" as WebexTeams
rectangle "API Gateway" as APIGateway
rectangle "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
rectangle "icanhazdadjoke.com" as JokeAPI

User -> WebexTeams: Mentions bot
WebexTeams -> APIGateway: Webhook POST
APIGateway -> Lambda: Invokes
Lambda -> JokeAPI: GET /joke
JokeAPI --> Lambda: Returns joke JSON
Lambda -> WebexTeams: POST /messages (with joke)
WebexTeams --> User: Displays joke

note right of Lambda
  Functions:
  - main()
  - getJoke()
  - postJoke()
end note

note right of APIGateway
  Configuration:
  - ROOMID
  - TOKEN
end note
@enduml